#: ..\..\fundamentals\request-features.rst:14
msgid "Feature interfaces"
msgstr ""

#: ..\..\fundamentals\request-features.rst:16
msgid ""
"ASP.NET 5 defines a number of `Http Feature Interfaces "
"<https://github.com/aspnet/HttpAbstractions/tree/1.0.0-beta5/src/Microsoft.AspNet.Http.Features>`_,"
" which are used by servers to identify which features they support. The most"
" basic features of a web server are the ability to handle requests and "
"return responses, as defined by the following feature interfaces:"
msgstr ""

#: ..\..\fundamentals\request-features.rst:19
msgid ""
"`IHttpRequestFeature "
"<https://github.com/aspnet/HttpAbstractions/blob/1.0.0-beta5/src/Microsoft.AspNet.Http.Features/IHttpRequestFeature.cs>`_"
msgstr ""

#: ..\..\fundamentals\request-features.rst:19
msgid ""
"Defines the structure of an HTTP request, including the protocol, path, "
"query string, headers, and body."
msgstr ""

#: ..\..\fundamentals\request-features.rst:22
msgid ""
"`IHttpResponseFeature "
"<https://github.com/aspnet/HttpAbstractions/blob/1.0.0-beta5/src/Microsoft.AspNet.Http.Features/IHttpResponseFeature.cs>`_"
msgstr ""

#: ..\..\fundamentals\request-features.rst:22
msgid ""
"Defines the structure of an HTTP response, including the status code, "
"headers, and body of the response."
msgstr ""

#: ..\..\fundamentals\request-features.rst:25
msgid ""
"`IHttpAuthenticationFeature "
"<https://github.com/aspnet/HttpAbstractions/blob/1.0.0-beta5/src/Microsoft.AspNet.Http.Features/Authentication/IHttpAuthenticationFeature.cs>`_"
msgstr ""

#: ..\..\fundamentals\request-features.rst:25
msgid ""
"Defines support for identifying users based on a ``ClaimsPrincipal`` and "
"specifying an authentication handler."
msgstr ""

#: ..\..\fundamentals\request-features.rst:28
msgid ""
"`IHttpUpgradeFeature "
"<https://github.com/aspnet/HttpAbstractions/blob/1.0.0-beta5/src/Microsoft.AspNet.Http.Features/IHttpUpgradeFeature.cs>`_"
msgstr ""

#: ..\..\fundamentals\request-features.rst:28
msgid ""
"Defines support for `HTTP Upgrades "
"<http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc2616#section-14.42>`_, which allow the client"
" to specify which additional protocols it would like to use if the server "
"wishes to switch protocols."
msgstr ""

#: ..\..\fundamentals\request-features.rst:31
msgid ""
"`IHttpBufferingFeature "
"<https://github.com/aspnet/HttpAbstractions/blob/1.0.0-beta5/src/Microsoft.AspNet.Http.Features/IHttpBufferingFeature.cs>`_"
msgstr ""

#: ..\..\fundamentals\request-features.rst:31
msgid "Defines methods for disabling buffering of requests and/or responses."
msgstr ""

#: ..\..\fundamentals\request-features.rst:34
msgid ""
"`IHttpConnectionFeature "
