msgid ""
"In the code above, the ``StaticFileContext`` class's ``SendAsync`` method "
"accesses the server's implementation of the ``IHttpSendFileFeature`` feature"
" (by calling ``GetFeature`` on HttpContext_). If the feature exists, it is "
"used to send the requested static file from its physical path. Otherwise, a "
"much slower workaround method is used to send the file (when available, the "
